Helix::Driver::DB::PostgreSQL, version 0.01
===========================================

The Helix::Driver::DB::PostgreSQL is the PostgreSQL database driver for 
Helix Framework. PostgreSQL versions 8.0+ are supported. 

INSTALLATION

To install the driver type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

To use this driver you must have the following packages installed:

    DBI
    DBD::Pg
    Helix

